\f0\b \cf0 \ul \ulc0 Travel Arrangements:
\f1 \

\f0 Inside the UK
\f1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri-7

\f0\b0 \cf0 \ulnone You will need to arrange your own transport to the airport and English Experience will arrange your outward and return flights. Please note: London Gatwick is the most commonly used airport, but flights may depart from another London airport. The details of your flights will be available to you on the online archive. We strongly recommend that if you are travelling by public transport to the airport you book tickets as soon as you have confirmation from us of your flight details, as the cost of tickets usually rises considerably if they are not booked well in advance of the travel date
\f1 .\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri-7

\f0\b \cf0 \ul \ulc0 Outside the UK
\f1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri-7

\f0\b0 \cf0 \ulnone Your Staff Data form states that you will be travelling from outside of the UK and therefore you will be making your own travel arrangements. Please book your travel and send us your travel details/receipts at least 1 month before the start of the camp
\f1 ,
\f0  and complete the attached Travel Expense Form. This enables us to inform the local coordinator of your arrival time and to make host family arrangements. You will not be required to make direct contact with your host family.\'a0 You are reimbursed your travel expenses (up to \'a3195, to include airport transfers) at the same time as receiving your wage. It is important that travel is booked early
\f1 ,
\f0  so please do not hesitate to contact the office at {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "mailto:campsadmin@paston.co.uk"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 campsadmin@paston.co.uk}} if you have any problems.
\f1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri-7

\f0\b \cf0 \ul \ulc0 On Line Archive
\f1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri-7

\f0\b0 \cf0 \ulnone All camp information will be provided on our online archive
\f1 ,
\f0  which will be updated once details are finalised. This will include travel information, camp information, the camp resource file and administrative forms. Once we have received your signed contract we will send you a link and issue you with a password in order to access the archive. We will not be sending you individual information
\f1 ,
\f0  so it is your responsibility to check the archive regularly for updates. \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri-7

