\pard\pardeftab720\ri-7

\b0 \cf0 \ulnone Suitable host family accommodation is arranged by the local coordinator
\f1 ,
\f0  based on the information you have provided us. Travel to meet your host family is arranged through us. Please note, we are unable to give you your host family details in advance to avoid conflicting arrangements. We therefore do not require you to make contact with them.
\f1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri-7

